{"version":3,"kind":"Article","sha256":"f50ec77ec452688b8563c44e62b5c457a49dec35801f9f8d3b48b6ed3476cb33","slug":"seismology.seismograph","location":"/seismology/seismograph.md","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"地震仪","content_includes_title":false,"github":"https://github.com/seismo-learn/seismology101","numbering":{"title":{"offset":1}},"source_url":"https://github.com/seismo-learn/seismology101/blob/main/source/seismology/seismograph.md","edit_url":"https://github.com/seismo-learn/seismology101/edit/main/source/seismology/seismograph.md","thumbnail":"/seismology101/build/seismograph-1993c64d3fa4788e80edaad2d145e4e9.jpg","exports":[{"format":"md","filename":"seismograph.md","url":"/seismology101/build/seismograph-b2e5a2c80fe36a04a67defb446cf0627.md"}]},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","children":[{"type":"list","ordered":false,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"本节贡献者: 姚家园、田冬冬","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"QukWD3W6kJ"}],"key":"kdF9Fzy6Nb"}],"key":"fXaILpG4Xv"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"最近更新日期: 2023-04-19","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1},"end":{"line":4,"column":1}},"key":"sFkQEqGfUp"}],"key":"To5Gi31vXP"}],"key":"etbOxrPL3b"}],"key":"aLyjXmOItE"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1},"end":{"line":6,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"基本原理","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1},"end":{"line":6,"column":1}},"key":"IhXn6pOsTm"}],"identifier":"id","label":"基本原理","html_id":"id","implicit":true,"key":"WzdcvVimc4"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1},"end":{"line":10,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"地震仪（seismograph）是检测和记录地面质点运动（位移、速度、加速度、转动等）的仪器，\n主要由地震计（seismometer）和数据记录系统组成。其中，地震计用于直接拾取地面运动并将其转换\n为符合数据记录系统需要的能量形式，而数据记录系统用于记录地面运动。","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1},"end":{"line":8,"column":1}},"key":"cWyIACgQtw"}],"key":"LOFCmsHG9z"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1},"end":{"line":16,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如以下卡通图所示，固定在地表的框架上挂有弹簧，并将重物悬挂在弹簧上，可以形象表示地震计；\n固定在框架上的旋转的鼓形象地代表了数据记录系统。当地球表面振动时，框架、弹簧、鼓随之移动，\n而重物悬浮不动。若在重物上固定一支笔，则地表和重物之间的相对运动就会被笔在旋转的鼓面上描绘出来，\n鼓面记录到的运动轨迹代表了地面质点运动，即地震图（seismogram）。可以看出，地震仪的基本原理\n是惯性定律。","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1},"end":{"line":12,"column":1}},"key":"NBh0leteWB"}],"key":"EwSOJzCQdM"},{"type":"container","kind":"figure","children":[{"type":"image","url":"/seismology101/build/seismograph-1993c64d3fa4788e80edaad2d145e4e9.jpg","alt":"地震仪的原理示意图","width":"50%","align":"center","urlSource":"seismograph.jpg","key":"eexZxGPaky"},{"type":"caption","children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":24,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"地震仪的原理示意图。引自\n","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"key":"knXmEA2ERk"},{"type":"link","url":"https://www.iris.edu/hq/inclass/fact-sheet/how_does_a_seismometer_work","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"How Does a Seismometer Work?","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"key":"UAANDRNI4o"}],"urlSource":"https://www.iris.edu/hq/inclass/fact-sheet/how_does_a_seismometer_work","key":"ue4lXgIfvS"}],"key":"tymahjHUFr"}],"key":"XmTbdb1WTK"}],"enumerator":"1","key":"vNIt1RN0ns"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"地震学研究中使用的地震仪对地面运动高度敏感，在非常安静的地区，甚至可以检测到 1 纳米的位移，\n几乎与原子间距一样小。大地震（如 2004 年印度尼西亚的苏门答腊地震）产生的地震波可以被全球范围\n的地震仪记录到，振幅高达到几厘米。","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"key":"LDUw0BGaBr"}],"key":"r6bBCBULQI"}],"key":"k2dNFWiNvm"}],"key":"giGKP7OtMW"},"references":{"cite":{"order":[],"data":{}}},"footer":{"navigation":{"prev":{"title":"地震图","url":"/seismology/seismogram","group":"地震学基础"},"next":{"title":"地震台站","url":"/seismology/station","group":"地震学基础"}}},"domain":"http://localhost:3000"}